00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:04,980
Qing, we'll miss you.

302
00:14:05,300 --> 00:14:06,230
Alright.

303
00:14:07,010 --> 00:14:08,140
No need to see me off.

304
00:14:09,010 --> 00:14:11,200
I made this medicine myself.

305
00:14:11,430 --> 00:14:12,430
Keep it well.

306
00:14:12,450 --> 00:14:14,450
It's effective for colds

307
00:14:14,540 --> 00:14:15,530
and headaches.

308
00:14:15,710 --> 00:14:16,420
Qing,

309
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:18,070
I can't treat you to a meal.

310
00:14:18,070 --> 00:14:19,200
Here are a few taels of silver.

311
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,130
Buy yourself some delicious food.

312
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:22,900
Thank you.

313
00:14:23,290 --> 00:14:25,800
Though we can't be fellow disciples,

314
00:14:25,830 --> 00:14:28,270
it's great to know you all.

315
00:14:31,590 --> 00:14:32,110
Bye.

316
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:33,430
-Bye.
-Bye.

317
00:14:33,430 --> 00:14:34,310
Take care.

318
00:14:37,710 --> 00:14:38,510
What's wrong?

319
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:39,910
I envy you

320
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:41,950
for having such companions.

321
00:14:42,990 --> 00:14:43,750
Don't be silly.

322
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:45,150
I'm your only companion.

323
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:47,020
Finding out where the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword is

324
00:14:47,020 --> 00:14:48,270
and staying alive

325
00:14:48,290 --> 00:14:49,720
is your top priority.

326
00:14:50,470 --> 00:14:51,390
Got it.

327
00:14:51,410 --> 00:14:52,780
Take care of yourself.

328
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:55,030
Don't always bully others.

329
00:14:55,410 --> 00:14:56,290
Except you,

330
00:14:56,450 --> 00:14:57,910
I won't bully anyone else.

331
00:15:00,470 --> 00:15:01,830
Take her as my disciple?

332
00:15:01,850 --> 00:15:02,650
That's right.

333
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:06,180
Dongfang Chunjiaoqing.

334
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:10,520
You remembered her name?

335
00:15:11,150 --> 00:15:12,370
Siqiong,

336
00:15:12,410 --> 00:15:14,060
as the No.1 in the world,

337
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:17,190
I'm afraid you don't know the struggles of ordinary people.

338
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:19,150
I'm from a normal family.

339
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:20,490
To get here,

340
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:23,520
I've made a lot of efforts than others.

341
00:15:23,630 --> 00:15:26,950
I know well the price I have to pay.

342
00:15:27,900 --> 00:15:30,180
I don't want to see ordinary children

343
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:32,440
struggle in the world.

344
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:36,040
So I won't take such disciples anymore.

345
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,710
Your eldest disciple

346
00:15:37,740 --> 00:15:39,270
is just like that, isn't it?

347
00:15:39,460 --> 00:15:40,020
I...

348
00:15:41,180 --> 00:15:44,340
I only allow myself to make the mistake once.

349
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:46,760
Since you've already made a mistake,

350
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:49,080
another one won't hurt.

351
00:15:50,180 --> 00:15:50,710
Then

352
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,750
what do you like about her?

353
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:54,900
She

354
00:15:55,930 --> 00:15:57,860
might become the No.1 in the world.

355
00:16:01,610 --> 00:16:02,330
Fine.

356
00:16:02,450 --> 00:16:03,960
You stay and look for the sword.

357
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,460
I'll stay in Qingshui Town to survive.

358
00:16:05,460 --> 00:16:06,310
What else?

359
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:07,840
Lu Zizheng,

360
00:16:07,870 --> 00:16:09,190
can you stop copying me?

361
00:16:09,190 --> 00:16:09,820
If you keep copying me,

362
00:16:09,820 --> 00:16:11,070
I'll really get mad.

363
00:16:11,830 --> 00:16:12,870
You're almost dead,

364
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:13,830
what's there to be afraid of?

365
00:16:13,830 --> 00:16:14,030
You...

366
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:14,630
Qing.

367
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:15,870
Bai.

368
00:16:16,090 --> 00:16:16,610
Qing.

369
00:16:16,630 --> 00:16:17,340
What's going on?

370
00:16:17,340 --> 00:16:17,780
Wait.

371
00:16:17,830 --> 00:16:19,230
Did they find something?

372
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,160
Get ready

373
00:16:20,190 --> 00:16:21,310
to run at any time.

374
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:22,660
I'm exhausted.

375
00:16:22,990 --> 00:16:23,900
Why are you two

376
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,090
walking so fast?

377
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:25,720
What's up?

378
00:16:26,830 --> 00:16:28,190
Go back with me.

379
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:29,280
Let's go.

380
00:16:29,820 --> 00:16:30,940
Why?

381
00:16:31,650 --> 00:16:32,970
Master

382
00:16:33,310 --> 00:16:35,200
accepts you as his disciple.

383
00:16:46,140 --> 00:16:47,300
Starting today,

384
00:16:47,350 --> 00:16:50,860
you two will be disciples of the Li San Hall of Xiling.

385
00:16:51,220 --> 00:16:53,870
You must follow Xiling's rules,

386
00:16:53,900 --> 00:16:55,170
to save people

387
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,480
and uphold justice.

388
00:16:56,880 --> 00:16:59,640
You must not betray your master,

389
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:02,570
and must keep your thoughts pure.

390
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,370
Remember,

391
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:07,099
Xiling disciples support each other,

392
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:08,790
and work together.

393
00:17:08,950 --> 00:17:11,349
Yes, Master.

394
00:17:14,010 --> 00:17:14,920
Siqiong,

395
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:16,099
say something.

396
00:17:17,540 --> 00:17:18,069
Good.

397
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:19,500
Keep it up.

398
00:17:25,069 --> 00:17:25,920
Quancai,

399
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:28,359
take them around

400
00:17:28,390 --> 00:17:30,440
to familiarize with Xiling,

401
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:33,350
and also tell them about Xiling.

402
00:17:34,150 --> 00:17:36,830
There have been eight halls since the founding of Xiling Sect:

403
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:38,830
Qian Yi Hall,

404
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:39,980
Dui Er Hall,

405
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:41,580
Li San Hall,

406
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:44,440
Zhen Si Hall, Xun Wu Hall, Kan Liu Hall,

407
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,840
Gen Qi Hall, and Kun Ba Hall.

408
00:17:47,570 --> 00:17:49,280
Great Master has nine disciples,

409
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:51,320
eight of whom are hall leaders,

410
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:54,170
and Master Ruan ranks ninth.

411
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:56,670
Fifteen years ago,

412
00:17:56,540 --> 00:18:00,730
[Grave of Xun Wu Hall's Zu Linmao] [Grave of Gen Qi Hall's Zhou Ming]

413
00:17:56,950 --> 00:17:58,710
Great Master led seven hall leaders

414
00:17:58,710 --> 00:18:01,520
to fight the Sacred Blood Sect, suffering heavy casualties.

415
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:03,780
After the war, five masters passed away,

416
00:18:03,910 --> 00:18:05,310
and two were missing.

417
00:18:06,990 --> 00:18:07,870
Only Master

418
00:18:08,340 --> 00:18:09,990
was unable to go because of his injury

419
00:18:09,990 --> 00:18:12,030
and survived.

420
00:18:13,190 --> 00:18:15,990
If Master Ruan hadn't become the No. 1 in the world,

421
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:18,510
Xiling would have fallen

422
00:18:19,670 --> 00:18:20,470
since then.

423
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:22,800
Xiling truly upholds justice.

424
00:18:23,180 --> 00:18:25,700
These heroes died honorably.

425
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:29,370
Died honorably? Easy for you to say.

426
00:18:29,410 --> 00:18:32,220
After that battle, Xiling lost a lot.

427
00:18:32,740 --> 00:18:34,540
That's why the disciples of other halls

428
00:18:34,540 --> 00:18:37,790
are under the unified teaching of Li San Hall's leader.

429
00:18:38,230 --> 00:18:39,380
That's why

430
00:18:39,670 --> 00:18:41,070
all disciples,

431
00:18:41,100 --> 00:18:42,540
new and old,

432
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:45,400
must pay respect to the five deceased masters.

433
00:18:43,250 --> 00:18:45,250
[Grave of Xun Wu Hall's Zu Linmao] [Grave of Gen Qi Hall's Zhou Ming]

434
00:18:48,860 --> 00:18:49,870
Without them,

435
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:54,270
Xiling wouldn't be stable today.

436
00:19:01,820 --> 00:19:03,150
What do you mean?

437
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:04,350
Are you not

438
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:06,490
sincerely joining Xiling?

439
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:10,720
I just thought of my deceased family.

440
00:19:10,800 --> 00:19:12,340
We haven't been home for a long time.

441
00:19:12,340 --> 00:19:13,940
We also want to worship them.

442
00:19:15,350 --> 00:19:17,340
This is the rule set by the Great Master.

443
00:19:17,340 --> 00:19:18,830
We start lessons at 5 a.m.

444
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:20,240
Medical studies in the morning,

445
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,950
martial arts in the afternoon,

446
00:19:21,950 --> 00:19:24,390
and take turns going down the mountain to treat people.

447
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:27,350
The consultation fee is for the maintenance of the sect.

448
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:29,710
Master Ruan teaches martial arts,

449
00:19:29,710 --> 00:19:32,430
and our master teaches medicine.

450
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:33,630
Alright,

451
00:19:33,660 --> 00:19:36,610
if there are no questions, let's go back.

452
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:38,800
Senior,

453
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:40,670
I have a question.

454
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:42,360
Go ahead.

455
00:19:42,990 --> 00:19:45,250
Why did Master suddenly change his mind?

456
00:19:45,250 --> 00:19:46,950
Was it my sincerity that moved him?

457
00:19:46,950 --> 00:19:47,980
Do you really want to know?

458
00:19:47,980 --> 00:19:48,800
Of course.

459
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:50,300
Go ask Master.

460
00:19:50,850 --> 00:19:51,960
Forget it.

461
00:19:55,750 --> 00:19:56,630
Uncle,

462
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,830
why are you thinner?

463
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:01,200
How have you been lately?

464
00:20:02,130 --> 00:20:04,390
It's been really hard, Uncle.

465
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:05,240
My legs...

466
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:05,950
Shaoyi.

467
00:20:06,230 --> 00:20:07,380
and my butt

468
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:09,350
-are worn out by the saddle.
-Shaoyi.

469
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:11,190
I miss you so much.

470
00:20:11,190 --> 00:20:12,970
Doctor, please just ignore him.

471
00:20:12,970 --> 00:20:13,610
Uncle,

472
00:20:14,190 --> 00:20:15,930
I'm most afraid of not seeing you.

473
00:20:15,930 --> 00:20:16,690
Shaoyi.

474
00:20:16,710 --> 00:20:18,810
I have nightmares every night.

475
00:20:18,830 --> 00:20:19,350
Uncle.

476
00:20:19,380 --> 00:20:20,110
Shaoyi,

477
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:21,350
you're overacting.

478
00:20:21,780 --> 00:20:23,460
So hypocritical.

479
00:20:25,950 --> 00:20:27,210
None of your business.

480
00:20:27,210 --> 00:20:28,710
You knocked me out last time.

481
00:20:28,710 --> 00:20:29,150
I...

482
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:30,950
I haven't got even with you yet.

483
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:32,570
I apologize.

484
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:36,240
So you are the guests of Changqing Chamber of Commerce.

485
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:39,520
Our Fire Crane Tribe

486
00:20:39,550 --> 00:20:43,260
had dealings with the Chamber of Commerce and Duan Residence a long time ago.

487
00:20:43,260 --> 00:20:45,590
To thank you for saving our young master,

488
00:20:45,630 --> 00:20:48,190
we have a small token of appreciation.

489
00:20:57,020 --> 00:20:57,740
Duan Mou,

490
00:20:57,830 --> 00:20:59,510
you're so rich.

491
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:00,740
Uncle,

492
00:21:00,760 --> 00:21:02,680
she doesn't think your name is Duan Mou, does she?

493
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:03,660
If it's not Duan Mou,

494
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:04,660
is it Re?

495
00:21:04,710 --> 00:21:05,430
Wu,

496
00:21:05,460 --> 00:21:06,410
don't be rude.

497
00:21:09,930 --> 00:21:12,190
Re means husband.

498
00:21:13,260 --> 00:21:14,460
That won't do.

499
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:15,930
You can't call my uncle Re.

500
00:21:15,930 --> 00:21:17,220
Should I call you then?

501
00:21:18,470 --> 00:21:19,960
It's not impossible.

502
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:21,470
Shaoyi.

503
00:21:21,710 --> 00:21:23,040
You can only be my slave.

504
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:25,740
This is the young master of the Duan family.

505
00:21:25,870 --> 00:21:26,930
Mind your manners.

506
00:21:28,010 --> 00:21:28,710
It's fine.

507
00:21:28,990 --> 00:21:29,820
It's fine.

508
00:21:30,630 --> 00:21:32,310
Since my family are here to pick me up,

509
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:33,040
doctor,

510
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:35,000
I'll leave now.

511
00:21:35,610 --> 00:21:36,790
Uncle,

512
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:39,120
you haven't fully recovered.

513
00:21:40,110 --> 00:21:41,440
I suggest

514
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:43,680
you should leave after you recover.

515
00:21:44,900 --> 00:21:45,850
Yes, young master.

516
00:21:45,850 --> 00:21:48,440
I think you should rest for a few more days.

517
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:31,750
I'm the first.

518
00:22:31,750 --> 00:22:32,590
Meat buns.

519
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:34,230
I got the meat buns first.

520
00:22:34,230 --> 00:22:35,630
I want some too.

521
00:22:35,670 --> 00:22:36,440
Don't push!

522
00:22:37,360 --> 00:22:39,200
No. 1 in the world?

523
00:22:39,670 --> 00:22:42,430
Since when did Siqiong start joking?

524
00:22:50,330 --> 00:22:51,090
Hey,

525
00:22:55,190 --> 00:22:56,400
I got the buns.

526
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:58,670
You adapted quite quickly.

527
00:22:59,370 --> 00:23:00,320
If we can't enjoy life,

528
00:23:00,320 --> 00:23:01,470
then we must adapt.

529
00:23:01,510 --> 00:23:03,270
We have to live comfortably.

530
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:06,320
Don't just think about adapting,

531
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:07,680
think about why you joined Xiling.

532
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:08,680
To find Qingmu...

533
00:23:11,260 --> 00:23:13,020
To find the sword and survive.

534
00:23:13,800 --> 00:23:14,710
I remember.

535
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:25,990
Senior,

536
00:23:26,040 --> 00:23:27,160
will this work?

537
00:23:27,520 --> 00:23:28,480
Whether it can or not,

538
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,480
we have to make it.

539
00:23:32,220 --> 00:23:34,220
I heard you know everything.

540
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:34,960
Is that true?

541
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:35,880
Of course.

542
00:23:36,050 --> 00:23:37,480
I know astronomy, geography.

543
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:39,040
and even bedroom secrets.

544
00:23:40,980 --> 00:23:42,260
Do you know Qingmu...

545
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,010
Master Ruan,

546
00:23:44,690 --> 00:23:45,590
can you help me check

547
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:47,310
if my second move of Flowing Water Sword is right?

548
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:48,870
Not bad. Keep it up.

549
00:23:49,140 --> 00:23:50,340
Look at Man Tianxing.

550
00:23:50,380 --> 00:23:53,990
-She has liked Master Ruan for a long time.
-I haven't started yet.

551
00:23:53,990 --> 00:23:55,900
What a pity.

552
00:23:55,920 --> 00:23:57,850
I think Master Ruan is quite warm.

553
00:23:57,920 --> 00:24:00,370
Isn't there any romantic gossip about him?

554
00:24:00,390 --> 00:24:02,830
Another woman blinded by illusions.

555
00:24:02,850 --> 00:24:04,800
Do you think anyone can be the No.1 in the world?

556
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:06,480
That position is built

557
00:24:06,580 --> 00:24:08,340
on countless corpses.

558
00:24:08,970 --> 00:24:11,880
Love and desires

559
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:14,690
don't deserve to disturb Master Ruan.

560
00:24:16,230 --> 00:24:17,930
Don't say I didn't warn you,

561
00:24:17,970 --> 00:24:19,770
people like Master Ruan

562
00:24:21,110 --> 00:24:22,210
can only be admired from a distance,

563
00:24:22,210 --> 00:24:23,160
not played with.

564
00:24:25,090 --> 00:24:27,320
It's normal to have emotions and desires.

565
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:28,850
Master Ruan is in his prime.

566
00:24:29,460 --> 00:24:31,960
Suppressing desires is abnormal.

567
00:24:32,460 --> 00:24:33,820
Dongfang Chunjiaoqing.

568
00:24:33,820 --> 00:24:34,340
Yes.

569
00:24:34,860 --> 00:24:37,270
Master Ruan remembers Qing's name.

570
00:24:41,610 --> 00:24:42,580
Master Ruan.

571
00:24:43,570 --> 00:24:44,610
You...

572
00:24:45,730 --> 00:24:47,140
look beautiful when you smile.

573
00:24:47,140 --> 00:24:49,790
Practice the second move of Flowing Water Sword ten times.

574
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:51,030
I'll check tomorrow.

575
00:24:53,290 --> 00:24:53,920
Yes.

576
00:24:56,600 --> 00:24:57,880
I'm exhausted.

577
00:24:58,710 --> 00:25:00,580
It's all my big mouth's fault,

578
00:25:00,670 --> 00:25:02,260
offending Master Ruan.

579
00:25:04,760 --> 00:25:05,840
Master. Master.

580
00:25:05,870 --> 00:25:08,550
You're quite comfortable with calling him that.

581
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:09,550
What else can I do?

582
00:25:09,700 --> 00:25:11,300
With our current situation,

583
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:12,370
what do you want?

584
00:25:13,210 --> 00:25:13,930
Alright,

585
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:16,190
in the next few days,

586
00:25:16,320 --> 00:25:17,510
we need to visit Tianlu Pavilion.

587
00:25:17,510 --> 00:25:18,680
Tianlu Pavilion?

588
00:25:18,730 --> 00:25:20,880
That's Xiling's sacred library.

589
00:25:21,350 --> 00:25:24,460
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

