592
00:25:28,300 --> 00:25:30,500
You better go there on your own.

593
00:25:30,530 --> 00:25:31,660
What else can you do?

594
00:25:31,910 --> 00:25:32,630
I...

595
00:25:36,620 --> 00:25:37,380
Uncle,

596
00:25:37,410 --> 00:25:38,570
let me tell you

597
00:25:38,600 --> 00:25:40,890
another really funny story.

598
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:41,830
If you laugh,

599
00:25:41,830 --> 00:25:42,980
your hand won't hurt anymore.

600
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:43,700
Once

601
00:25:43,740 --> 00:25:44,700
upon a time...

602
00:25:44,940 --> 00:25:45,520
Wu,

603
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:46,750
come here and listen.

604
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:51,810
What's the matter?

605
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:53,080
What is it?

606
00:25:58,780 --> 00:25:59,430
Here.

607
00:26:17,630 --> 00:26:18,450
Thank you.

608
00:26:18,730 --> 00:26:20,520
I was angry that you bought me from the Moon Wolf Tribe.

609
00:26:20,520 --> 00:26:22,040
I thought you were not a good person,

610
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:23,700
so I wouldn't be polite to you.

611
00:26:23,850 --> 00:26:25,300
But now that I think about it,

612
00:26:25,300 --> 00:26:26,560
if you hadn't saved me,

613
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:28,250
I would have been dead.

614
00:26:28,580 --> 00:26:29,420
Speaking of which,

615
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:30,460
you are my savior.

616
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,900
After I fell off the cliff,

617
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:33,060
you treated me.

618
00:26:33,370 --> 00:26:35,520
I guess we're even now.

619
00:26:36,750 --> 00:26:38,230
So why did you

620
00:26:38,260 --> 00:26:40,260
buy slaves from the Moon Wolf Tribe?

621
00:26:42,750 --> 00:26:44,110
It's someone I know.

622
00:26:44,790 --> 00:26:45,790
She went missing.

623
00:26:47,020 --> 00:26:48,220
Someone told me

624
00:26:48,710 --> 00:26:50,710
she might be in the Moon Wolf Tribe's

625
00:26:51,250 --> 00:26:52,380
slave trade.

626
00:26:53,050 --> 00:26:54,180
What happened next?

627
00:26:56,260 --> 00:26:58,040
Go on.

628
00:26:58,420 --> 00:26:59,290
What next?

629
00:26:59,300 --> 00:27:00,360
Uncle, take a rest.

630
00:27:00,510 --> 00:27:01,160
Come out with me.

631
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:01,730
I'll tell you what happened next.

632
00:27:01,730 --> 00:27:02,140
No.

633
00:27:02,170 --> 00:27:02,690
Come on.

634
00:27:03,140 --> 00:27:03,670
Come on.

635
00:27:03,900 --> 00:27:04,590
Let me tell you.

636
00:27:04,590 --> 00:27:05,940
I'll tell you a good story.

637
00:27:05,940 --> 00:27:06,470
Let's go.

638
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:19,900
I see.

639
00:27:20,330 --> 00:27:23,390
So there's actually a misunderstanding between them.

640
00:27:24,510 --> 00:27:25,190
So,

641
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:28,990
where is Gu Qingqiao now?

642
00:27:29,010 --> 00:27:30,090
I don't know.

643
00:27:30,590 --> 00:27:31,310
I thought

644
00:27:31,310 --> 00:27:33,780
she might appear in the Moon Wolf Tribe's slave trade,

645
00:27:33,780 --> 00:27:35,620
but found you instead.

646
00:27:36,710 --> 00:27:38,840
No wonder Mr. Duan has been chasing me.

647
00:27:39,450 --> 00:27:40,650
Does she look like me?

648
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:41,790
No.

649
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:43,930
You're much prettier than her.

650
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:44,890
You're sweet.

651
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:52,120
How about

652
00:27:52,300 --> 00:27:53,990
you be my slave from now on?

653
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:56,210
If you become my slave,

654
00:27:56,230 --> 00:27:58,290
you'll have to obey me in everything.

655
00:28:01,140 --> 00:28:01,820
Master.

656
00:28:02,380 --> 00:28:03,440
Have some chicken.

657
00:28:35,010 --> 00:28:35,890
Master Ruan,

658
00:28:36,690 --> 00:28:40,740
why are you still up so late?

659
00:28:40,840 --> 00:28:42,200
It's cold at night.

660
00:28:42,230 --> 00:28:43,490
You might catch a cold.

661
00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:44,770
I can't sleep.

662
00:28:44,810 --> 00:28:46,030
Neither can I.

663
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:49,650
I thought I'm the only one who couldn't sleep.

664
00:28:50,100 --> 00:28:51,300
Why can't you sleep?

665
00:28:51,320 --> 00:28:52,650
There are too many worries.

666
00:28:52,650 --> 00:28:55,510
When I close my eyes, I see people I don't want to see.

667
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:56,630
What about you?

668
00:28:56,630 --> 00:28:57,960
I have no distractions.

669
00:28:58,130 --> 00:28:59,390
No one enters my dream.

670
00:28:59,470 --> 00:29:00,500
As time goes by,

671
00:29:00,870 --> 00:29:03,330
I can't fall asleep even with my eyes closed.

672
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:06,200
Why not enjoy the beauty of the world

673
00:29:06,650 --> 00:29:08,780
during the long night?

674
00:29:09,660 --> 00:29:11,350
We are the opposite.

675
00:29:11,850 --> 00:29:13,390
You have nothing on your mind,

676
00:29:13,390 --> 00:29:14,840
while I have too much.

677
00:29:14,860 --> 00:29:16,260
I wish we could switch.

678
00:29:16,990 --> 00:29:17,830
Master Ruan,

679
00:29:18,030 --> 00:29:20,050
if there's nothing else,

680
00:29:20,250 --> 00:29:21,570
I'll go back first.

681
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:24,190
Qing.

682
00:29:25,670 --> 00:29:27,100
Since you can't sleep,

683
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:28,340
how about...

684
00:29:28,380 --> 00:29:29,180
Master Ruan,

685
00:29:29,300 --> 00:29:30,470
after you left today,

686
00:29:30,470 --> 00:29:31,950
I practiced until sunset

687
00:29:32,020 --> 00:29:33,680
without the slightest slack.

688
00:29:33,690 --> 00:29:37,050
But that Flowing Water Sword is too difficult.

689
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:38,440
I'm slow-witted,

690
00:29:39,510 --> 00:29:40,470
and started late.

691
00:29:40,470 --> 00:29:42,740
Could you give me two more days?

692
00:29:42,910 --> 00:29:44,070
I wanted to ask you

693
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:46,330
if you could stay and have a drink with me.

694
00:29:46,750 --> 00:29:48,070
You're so self-aware.

695
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:50,190
Follow me.

696
00:30:38,100 --> 00:30:40,490
Flowing Water Style is not a strong sword technique.

697
00:30:40,490 --> 00:30:42,350
It's about leveraging strength.

698
00:31:33,650 --> 00:31:34,610
Immortal?

699
00:31:38,430 --> 00:31:39,220
Are you serious?

700
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,260
Take it easy.

701
00:31:40,350 --> 00:31:41,670
A man and a woman alone late at night,

702
00:31:41,670 --> 00:31:42,800
quite enjoyed, huh?

703
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:44,350
You don't know,

704
00:31:44,630 --> 00:31:47,450
Master Ruan is so handsome when playing sword,

705
00:31:47,470 --> 00:31:48,640
like an immortal.

706
00:31:48,670 --> 00:31:49,460
Look at you.

707
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:50,520
A totally lovesick fool.

708
00:31:50,520 --> 00:31:51,120
No,

709
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:54,140
I just thought of Duan Yu's sword playing,

710
00:31:55,090 --> 00:31:56,730
also like an immortal.

711
00:31:58,080 --> 00:31:59,810
You really are a lovesick fool.

712
00:32:00,690 --> 00:32:01,280
I...

713
00:32:07,620 --> 00:32:08,420
Let go.

714
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:09,620
Apologize.

715
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:11,220
Are you a dog? Let go.

716
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:12,160
Apologize.

717
00:32:12,630 --> 00:32:13,780
Admit it.

718
00:32:20,150 --> 00:32:22,590
While you were together with Ruan Siqiong last night,

719
00:32:22,590 --> 00:32:25,020
I searched the entire Xiling Sect.

720
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:26,240
I did find something.

721
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:27,200
What did you find?

722
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:27,830
I found

723
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:30,000
there is a forbidden area in Xiling.

724
00:32:30,040 --> 00:32:30,750
Where is it?

725
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:31,660
Forbidden area.

726
00:32:31,660 --> 00:32:32,570
I know.

727
00:32:32,600 --> 00:32:33,480
What's its name?

728
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:34,520
Forbidden area.

729
00:32:35,670 --> 00:32:36,950
Speak well.

730
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:43,450
[Forbidden Area]

731
00:32:47,670 --> 00:32:48,930
Did you see it clearly?

732
00:32:50,650 --> 00:32:51,860
This is too straightfoward.

733
00:32:51,860 --> 00:32:53,920
What are you two sneaking around for?

734
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:55,370
This is Xiling's forbidden area.

735
00:32:55,370 --> 00:32:56,330
No trespassing.

736
00:32:57,740 --> 00:32:58,690
Senior,

737
00:32:58,970 --> 00:33:00,730
what is inside

738
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:02,780
