739
00:33:02,990 --> 00:33:06,400
It's said that there are traps and monsters who eat humans.

740
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:10,190
It's said that there are traps and monsters who eat humans?

741
00:33:10,410 --> 00:33:12,700
So you've never seen it?

742
00:33:13,050 --> 00:33:13,340
I...

743
00:33:13,380 --> 00:33:14,740
If I had seen it,

744
00:33:14,930 --> 00:33:16,800
