745
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:18,920
You not only have a small body

746
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,590
but also a small brain.

747
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:24,230
Now leave.

748
00:33:24,890 --> 00:33:25,710
Go.

749
00:33:25,730 --> 00:33:26,290
Okay.

750
00:33:29,630 --> 00:33:32,890
I'll go to the Tianlu Pavilion to check the forbidden area.

751
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:54,170
Black Wood Human-shaped Sword is a sacred object of Xiling.

752
00:33:54,870 --> 00:33:57,740
It must be recorded in the sect's history books.

753
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:10,270
[Xiling Chronicles]

754
00:34:10,300 --> 00:34:11,790
[Xiling Chronicles, Volume II]

755
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:12,290
[Xiling Records]

756
00:34:22,020 --> 00:34:25,100
That year, in an ordinary village,

757
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:29,560
a baby named Wang Tianshan was born.

758
00:34:29,590 --> 00:34:31,670
No one knew then

759
00:34:31,699 --> 00:34:35,850
that the world would change because of him.

760
00:34:40,510 --> 00:34:43,969
That year, Wang Tianshan led Xiling Sect against Nanming Sect

761
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:46,100
in a sword competition,

762
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:48,960
being invincible,

763
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,400
crushing all opponents.

764
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,659
That old man Wang Tianshan

765
00:34:53,659 --> 00:34:55,460
always boasting about himself.

766
00:34:56,870 --> 00:34:58,950
Who is speaking ill of me?

767
00:35:14,190 --> 00:35:16,590
No one but the sect leader is allowed

768
00:35:16,610 --> 00:35:18,010
