769
00:35:18,710 --> 00:35:19,540
Excuse me,

770
00:35:19,940 --> 00:35:20,850
sir.

771
00:35:20,890 --> 00:35:22,840
I'm a new disciple.

772
00:35:22,870 --> 00:35:25,030
I'm trying to catch up with my seniors,

773
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:26,330
so I came to study hard.

774
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:29,260
I heard the books on the top floor are very valuable,

775
00:35:29,260 --> 00:35:30,590
so I came to borrow them.

776
00:35:34,220 --> 00:35:36,480
No one but the sect leader is allowed

777
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,100
inside Tianlu Pavilion.

778
00:35:38,730 --> 00:35:39,860
Sorry to bother you.

779
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:48,020
Senior,

780
00:35:48,040 --> 00:35:50,350
do you know what the Xiling's forbidden area is?

781
00:35:50,350 --> 00:35:51,630
You know it too?

782
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:55,150
I saw it while wandering around.

783
00:35:55,350 --> 00:35:56,810
It looks very mysterious.

784
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:59,730
Do you think there are treasures inside?

785
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,910
The forbidden area has always been mysterious.

786
00:36:01,910 --> 00:36:04,190
Except for the Great Master, Master and Master Ruan,

787
00:36:04,190 --> 00:36:05,710
no one else can enter,

788
00:36:06,190 --> 00:36:08,160
so we don't know what's inside.

789
00:36:08,790 --> 00:36:12,820
But it's said there are some dangerous traps,

790
00:36:12,940 --> 00:36:13,650
monsters,

791
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:15,500
and treasures.

792
00:36:15,710 --> 00:36:16,670
Treasures?

793
00:36:16,790 --> 00:36:18,230
Dongfang Chunjiaoqing.

794
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,520
Even Mala

795
00:36:22,080 --> 00:36:23,780
knows you now?

796
00:36:24,350 --> 00:36:26,580
When I was recovering here,

797
00:36:26,600 --> 00:36:28,020
I chatted with it.

798
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:30,930
Senior,

799
00:36:30,950 --> 00:36:33,610
isn't it inappropriate for us to go in like this?

800
00:36:34,090 --> 00:36:35,960
When Master Ruan isn't in Xiling,

801
00:36:35,990 --> 00:36:38,050
we often come to feed the bird for him.

802
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:42,650
Senior,

803
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:44,670
do you like Master Ruan?

804
00:36:45,340 --> 00:36:46,020
Yes.

805
00:36:46,060 --> 00:36:47,310
So honest.

806
00:36:47,740 --> 00:36:49,500
It's not shameful to like him.

807
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:50,920
I don't need to hide it.

808
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:54,500
Mala.

809
00:36:56,300 --> 00:36:57,940
Dongfang Chunjiaoqing.

810
00:37:05,550 --> 00:37:06,920
[Forbidden Area]

811
00:37:08,580 --> 00:37:09,880
Xiling's forbidden area.

812
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:11,000
No trespassing.

813
00:37:11,330 --> 00:37:12,340
[Forbidden Area]

814
00:37:35,970 --> 00:37:40,860
[Forbidden Area]

815
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:47,930
Bai,

816
00:37:48,190 --> 00:37:49,640
why didn't you wake me up?

817
00:37:49,660 --> 00:37:51,120
I've been waiting for you.

818
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:52,790
I'll call you next time.

819
00:37:52,790 --> 00:37:54,790
Bai, you don't look well.

820
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:56,350
Let me check your pulse.

821
00:37:56,350 --> 00:37:57,610
None of your business.

822
00:37:59,990 --> 00:38:01,390
Thanks for your concern.

823
00:38:01,460 --> 00:38:02,590
