824
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:04,470
Go to sleep.

825
00:38:26,330 --> 00:38:27,790
There's no one here.

826
00:38:27,900 --> 00:38:29,470
God bless me.

827
00:38:30,150 --> 00:38:31,350
Tomorrow I will tell Bai

828
00:38:31,350 --> 00:38:32,550
