829
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:34,590
and scare him.

830
00:38:36,470 --> 00:38:37,350
What have you done?

831
00:38:37,350 --> 00:38:38,380
Ghost!

832
00:38:39,520 --> 00:38:40,780
No internal injuries.

833
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:42,390
It shouldn't be her.

834
00:38:43,620 --> 00:38:44,950
What are you doing here?

835
00:38:44,990 --> 00:38:46,090
I...

836
00:38:46,430 --> 00:38:47,890
I'm here to study all night.

837
00:38:47,890 --> 00:38:49,440
Don't you know that disciples

838
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:51,100
are not allowed to enter here?

839
00:38:51,570 --> 00:38:52,650
I don't know.

840
00:38:52,820 --> 00:38:53,990
I saw the lights on

841
00:38:54,070 --> 00:38:55,310
and the door wasn't locked,

842
00:38:55,310 --> 00:38:56,230
so I came in.

843
00:38:57,090 --> 00:38:58,930
I'm leaving now.
